    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car, keeping it polished and pristine inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that wonderful fresh feel. I\u2019m really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be obsessed with it. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
